  <div class="container">
    <section class="content">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <p>
        I&apos;m Matt Bidewell, a software engineer with {yearsExp}+ years of
        experience building products on the web.
      </p>
      <p>
        I currently work as a Senior Software Engineer at{" "}
        <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.contentful.com/">
          Contentful
        </a>, and I enjoy shipping reliable systems, writing clearly, and working
        in the open.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can find me on{" "}
        <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://x.com/MattBidewell">
          X (formerly Twitter)
        </a>, browse my work on{" "}
        <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.github.com/mattbidewell">
          GitHub
        </a>, or connect via{" "}
        <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/matt-bidewell-a4578790/">
          LinkedIn
        </a>.
      </p>
      <p>
